org.drip.param.market

Class ComponentMultiMeasureQuote

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.service.stream.Serializer
      • org.drip.param.definition.ComponentQuote
        • org.drip.param.market.ComponentMultiMeasureQuote

  • public class ComponentMultiMeasureQuote
extends ComponentQuote
    This class holds the different types of quotes for a given component. It contains a single market field/quote pair, but multiple alternate named quotes (to accommodate quotes on different measures for the component).
